RootTools is a tool under Android phone for users who has the personalized requirements. The goal is to help Android users have the better phones and be outside from the impact and distress. 

RootTools can help you: 

    1. Delete in-system applications. All things in system are depend on yourself.
    2. Backup or restore applications and data, no longer afraid of flash the device. 
    3. Manage the components in applications. e.g. you do not want to see ads. 
    4. Always knows what the system running, and helps cleanup memory and keep the system smooth. 
    5. Intelligent Hosts modification. 
    6. More features are waiting for your opinion.

Please send your suggestions to us and it may help us making the better product. 
